":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"I know it's luxurious, but honestly, I don't really want to"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["use the park's restroom because it's a Japanese-style one.\""]},{"code":232,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,0,0,1,30,31,100,100,0,0,30,false]},{"code":108,"indent":0,"parameters":["//基本絵"]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[180]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"a_cg_06",0,0,0,60,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,0,0,0,0,60,100,100,255,0,60,true]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[178]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Well... to be honest, I've reached my limit of endurance, so there's"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["no other choice.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Sigh... If I could have held it in until I found a proper"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["restroom, there would have been no need to use this one...\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"But... there's no point in complaining, is there?\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"If you're going to do that, it's more important to finish using the"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["restroom as quickly as possible.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"...Hmm, mmmh...\""]},{"code":108,"indent":0,"parameters":["//aと放尿音"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"a_cg_06a",0,0,0,60,100,100,255,0]},{"code":250,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"お漏らし","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Hmm... Ah, mmm.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Peeing in a Japanese-style toilet. Even though I'm not doing anything"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["weird, why do I strangely feel a mysterious and strange sensation?\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"I feel like I'm doing something naughty even though it's"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["absolutely not true... Am I tired, maybe?\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"But I'm really feeling strange... No, no, I need to calm"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["down. It's absurd to do something naughty in the restroom!\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Anyway, I need to finish quickly and get out of here. If I stay in a"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["place like this for too long, I might end up doing something wrong.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Mmm... Ahh... I held it in for so long, so there's a lot coming out..."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Ahh.\""]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[14,"黒バック背景",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[8,"黒バック背景",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":0,"parameters":[65]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[14]},{"code":251,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Rio, feeling the urge to urinate, entered the Japanese-style"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["restroom in the park. Although it was a normal bodily"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["function, she couldn't help but feel a strange sensation,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["which left her feeling confused. However, she successfully finished using the restroom and quickly left to go outside."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["A minor problem. It may seem puzzling to others, but there"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["is no doubt that it was a big problem for Rio."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Well, since it ended without any issues, there is no point"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["in saying this and that. I simply urinated in the park"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["toilet. In short, that's the whole story!"]},{"code":221,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[8]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[199]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[180]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[133,133,1]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[189]},{"code":111,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,68,0]},{"code":108,"indent":1,"parameters":["特殊エリアに居るので、ここで回想をしても意味はない"]},{"code":408,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":408,"indent":1,"parameters":["きちんと正規の方法でないと解禁スイッチは押されない"]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":411,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":121,"indent":1,"parameters":[76,76,0]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[19,19,0]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[15,15,1]},{"code":355,"indent":0,"parameters":["EraseLoopPicture(5);"]},{"code":355,"indent":0,"parameters":["$gameScreen.clearPictures();"]},{"code":108,"indent":0,"parameters":["上記のスクリプトはピクチャを全部消す"]},{"code":408,"indent":0,"parameters":["一般の奴で著作とかは記載の必要はない"]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,46,5,8,2,0]},{"cod